--
-- Name: articles articles_id_pk; Type: CONSTRAINT; Schema: public; Owner: postgres
--

ALTER TABLE ONLY articles
    ADD CONSTRAINT articles_id_pk PRIMARY KEY (id);


--
-- Name: concepts concepts_pkey; Type: CONSTRAINT; Schema: public; Owner: postgres
--

ALTER TABLE ONLY concepts
    ADD CONSTRAINT concepts_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id);


--
-- Name: news_sources news_sources_pkey; Type: CONSTRAINT; Schema: public; Owner: postgres
--

ALTER TABLE ONLY news_sources
    ADD CONSTRAINT news_sources_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id);


--
-- Name: concepts_id_uindex; Type: INDEX; Schema: public; Owner: postgres
--

CREATE UNIQUE INDEX concepts_id_uindex ON concepts USING btree (id);


--
-- Name: news_sources_id_uindex; Type: INDEX; Schema: public; Owner: postgres
--

CREATE UNIQUE INDEX news_sources_id_uindex ON news_sources USING btree (id);


--
-- Name: concepts concepts_articles_id_fk; Type: FK CONSTRAINT; Schema: public; Owner: postgres
--

ALTER TABLE ONLY concepts
    ADD CONSTRAINT concepts_articles_id_fk FOREIGN KEY (article_id) REFERENCES articles(id) ON UPDATE CASCADE ON DELETE CASCADE;
